headline: Xcel Energy’s Monticello Nuclear Plant Receives Federal Approval to Extend Operations
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, January 02, 2025--Xcel Energy will extend the operation of its carbon-free Monticello Nuclear Generating Plant well into the future to support its clean energy vision, following the recent renewal of the plant’s operating license by the U.S. Nuclear Regulatory Commission (NRC).
